gmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"你班人 係講緊你呢班一碌鳩打沉一船人嗰班人呀<br />\n醒未呀柒頭<br />\n香港而家抗爭緊有邊個唔知<br />\n咁我問返你<br />\n咁你叫本身喺連登派開膠嘅去邊到喘息？<br />\n我都忍左好撚耐唔派<br />\n你個撚樣而家喺到分化真手足？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登手足會玩分化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你...唔撚通你個老母係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"之前試過俾人話起底咁多膠post實係港豬我真係屌佢老母你睇吓我幾撚時有喺有行動嗰陣發癲<br />\n反而啲冷氣軍師睇住live十鳩幾個post咁指揮就做咗好多嘢<br />\n開post自爆又屌自爆 唔開post自爆又屌港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"有時唔可以比班冷氣軍師 呀 Sor 可能或者係前線勇武但一路reply住連登一路抗爭緊又同時搞緊分化嘅奶奶奶太撚獨大<br />\n咁樣同違背三權分立主義嘅本質基本上冇乜撚野咩分別<br />\n你要記得上得連登嘅有好多都係中學雞<br />\n長年累月行動post搞到好似每月一篇咁係會疲倦<br />\n我就唔撚信幾個鳩post嘅能力足以令運動崩潰<br />\n適當嘅鳩post係有助放鬆心情架屌你老母<br />\n你估人人都好似扑縮咁撚有錢去寒國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你叫本身喺連登開鳩post同睇鳩post嗰班人去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱唔啱聽先屌你個奶咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccda42d0fd6fe3ff867fe15be2706a56d7131787","tid":1801180,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30aff96507331f5e596c5120d2c572d38e4966f4","tid":1801180,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fde680ad49c7e83078c872cb38424d693e578ff","tid":1801180,"uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{